or there lives ! And with use of there songs manage to escape ! But the one seeked was found in a Inn at the docks ! Scared and inspired by fear he hide behind many people ! And as I got close to him his skin pilled off, his blood boiled, his brain fried, and darkness engulfed him ! So I took his head and went my way ! But my fear stayed in Freeport forever ! As for poor Sir Edwin Motte ! His head stays in the pouch of my Master Kazen Fecae ! For that day Freeport will Never forget the terror I left behind. And the blood I spilled ! But I will return to kill the rest of them ! For they quiver in fear at the Very mention of my name ! But don't speak it too loud in Freeport or around druids and treants ! For they my attack you thinking I have returned. And out of fear they might even run from you ! For it is good to be evil ! And evil is good to be ! Walk well in the light ! For when I come the light fades to darkness. And darkness fades to death. And death fades to the void. And in void all Would be heroes lay. Fearing the day I send the rest to them ! So walk well my Brothers and sisters ! For I am the Terror of Norrath !)<br>
<br>
Xatrekik Terrorizer <br>
The Terror of Norrath ! <br>
<br>
Be safe all !  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/bexodusfellowshipforum.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hiking>Hiking</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(11/18/02 5:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/classes/c_shadow.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Tale of Terror</span><hr size=1> Xatrekik!<br>
<br>
We need to talk!  I have been long in the halls of my master Cazic Thule, but at his command, I have returned to Norrath to assemble my army.  I am in need of Generals, and it sounds like you may indeed be powerful enough to assist me.  We must slaughter the Fellowship, and conjure their bones to join our ranks.  Such are my orders.  <br>
<br>
So, Xatrekik, decide quickly, for I will not ask again - join me or suffer the fate of the rest of the Fellowship.<br>
<br>
Hiking<br>
Commander of the Undead Army of Exodus Fellowship <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/bexodusfellowshipforum.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xatrekik>Xatrekik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(11/20/02 1:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Tale of Terror</span><hr size=1> My Dear Dark Friend of Pain. I am the Terror of Norrath ! Fear flows through the great cities like water through a river ! And as I walk the streets of my dead foes I grin at the site of there death ! But I follow no servent but only the Great Cazic - Thule ! But I am always looking for &lt;coughs&gt; Partners that would be willing to kill the &quot;Would be Heroes&quot; by my side ! For I command the undead and the undead listen well to me ! <br>
<br>
For that is all today !<br>
<br>
